; Regression test for issue #1134: There is no --format-* option for xact
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1134
;
; The xact command should respect --format when specified.

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test xact --format '%(format_date(date, "%Y-%m-%d")) %(account) %(quantity(scrub(display_amount)))\n' 2024/02/01 Payee 20
2024-02-01 Expenses:Food 20
2024-02-01 Assets:Cash -20
end test
